{"tid":455281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"博多去熊本, 新幹線一定要買指定席?","createTime":"2017-11-02T02:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T15:57:21.000Z","uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"075cac7173066261d933f0ef24015c396b128a5a","tid":455281,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"唔係好明佢個price<br />\n如果就咁買自由席, 係唔係2130yen?<br />\n<br />\nor一定要買特急劵?<br />\n<br />\n點解又有分指定同自由席? (同價錢?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg&h=a9d84853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bec3dd807b827509d7459d3647339b2b44d09c6","tid":455281,"uid":66680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"如果你連續幾日搭 不如買北九州pass 可以任坐自由席同埋限次數嘅指定席"},{"pid":"084e959e08e3c5bc234e5b9bc78f68682551145a","tid":455281,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好明佢個price<br />\n如果就咁買自由席, 係唔係2130yen?<br />\n<br />\nor一定要買特急劵?<br />\n<br />\n點解又有分指定同自由席? (同價錢?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg&h=a9d84853&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔駛理佢 拆開果舊野 點都係特急指定<br />\n自由非特急呢d 野係新幹線唔存在<br />\n雖然我都唔明點解佢地要咁detail 寫出黎但其實冇果個option"},{"pid":"3d9fa767f2bb17455f5fb06249751946f3dda094","tid":455281,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"自由席車費係乘車券2130羊加自由席2480羊，總共4610羊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b6be06b6ddc377e40ee7a8ceb606d04c3cfe89","tid":455281,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"其實可以考慮巴士"},{"pid":"af4cdd55a787bfe9e3d7f13184e099e9a79e0c00","tid":455281,"uid":5542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"用pass 座指定席 ，單程咁買其實可以自由席都有位座 部車無乜人"},{"pid":"20f789f093705a1bca4375d1488656a98f9125a2","tid":455281,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用pass 座指定席 ，單程咁買其實可以自由席都有位座 部車無乜人</blockquote><br />\n但係都要買特急劵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7c4e73ca4fd1daab9d70a17fc0caa3ebf31ace","tid":455281,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bff10982a8918d59fa5d3bf3777b307eba5212","tid":455281,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"可以任坐<br />\n紅色嗰個詞係&quot;有&quot;，後面話用啦既意思"},{"pid":"352c112a05a609e87a111dee03bb6ac10698f0e0","tid":455281,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"我建議新幹線<br />\n其他方法坐好耐浪費時間"},{"pid":"9ea2282aab9ad1f6dc09c67623d667cb05d2da9d","tid":455281,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚去熊本城<br />\n無野睇的 省返日去第度好過"},{"pid":"4dbb6c38856a692b79863f0d021edd63c2f5d954","tid":455281,"uid":91720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:26:01.000Z","msg":"乘車卷 ~ 你由博多去熊本既火車錢<br />\n<br />\n特急卷 ~ 你坐新幹線要加既錢<br />\n<br />\n指定席 ~ 指定坐位唔會無位坐<br />\n<br />\n自由席 ~ 有幾卡車箱可以揾位坐，無位就要企成程<br />\n<br />\n指定席同自由席個價差唔遠<br />\n<br />\n不過一定要買特急劵"},{"pid":"d3500625743333ccaaf3b8f54cef3c3b420f2125","tid":455281,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好明佢個price<br />\n如果就咁買自由席, 係唔係2130yen?<br />\n<br />\nor一定要買特急劵?<br />\n<br />\n點解又有分指定同自由席? (同價錢?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F104603_9d37d2dec83919d3fa3fb136eaa9d58a.jpg&h=a9d84853&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/133646_d416299c39a3bc09aa6e17a7d9d2e35b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F133646_d416299c39a3bc09aa6e17a7d9d2e35b.jpg&h=1a4bc62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乗車券=車飛價錢<br />\n特急券=服務費（行快咗咪要收返你錢）&larr; 搭得新幹線就要買"},{"pid":"62aff86440e0e4d0cf90da8ef5ace6ccb96e3896","tid":455281,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我坐過反方向<br />\n記得有經熊本城<br />\n視乎你住邊<br />\n嗰次我住熊本通町筋同福岡天神嗰邊，兩度都要再轉車先去到JR站，計埋轉車時間，巴士只係慢半個鐘，又平咁多，大行李又可以放車底，結果唔諗新幹線"},{"pid":"b7f3c7b20006f918dfed7caea3a3fa801d8d0181","tid":455281,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我坐過反方向<br />\n記得有經熊本城<br />\n視乎你住邊<br />\n嗰次我住熊本通町筋同福岡天神嗰邊，兩度都要再轉車先去到JR站，計埋轉車時間，巴士只係慢半個鐘，又平咁多，大行李又可以放車底，結果唔諗新幹線</blockquote><br />\n新幹線嘅好處係用pass包埋，同埋福岡-熊本用嗰架列車內籠好有特色<br />\n如果你出發/目的地都係JR站附近，就新幹線啦<br />\n我揀咗巴士係因為上述原因，我住熊本日航酒店，個巴士站喺正門口。當然巴士都有pass，福岡-熊本嘅班次亦好密"},{"pid":"1c6122801947c6e6be942b6b87f06766b47ca8cb","tid":455281,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚去熊本城<br />\n無野睇的 省返日去第度好過</blockquote><br />\n地震復修冇咁快<br />\n係咪仲未有得入去睇？<br />\n調整好預期先去，就會冇咁失望嘅"},{"pid":"53a0668eec0111f6f051a411681461f135b06f34","tid":455281,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實可以考慮巴士</blockquote><br />\n而家睇緊<br />\n博多站3F -&gt; 熊本交通巴士站<br />\n2個幾鐘, 仲可以用SunQ pass<br />\n<br />\n一落車行過去就係熊本城, 唔洗再另外坐車<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪撚去熊本城<br />\n無野睇的 省返日去第度好過</blockquote><br />\n諗住去熊本附近周圍行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個咩上下通, 係咪同普通一條通菜街咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414fbc11de5d7b967bda2a761a58e36574fa855e","tid":455281,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係好明佢個price<br />\n如果就咁買自由席, 係唔係2130yen?<br />\n<br />\nor一定要買特急劵?<br />\n<br />\n點解又有分指定同自由席? (同價錢?)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"ht